This project focuses on building an end-to-end data analytics pipeline to evaluate the performance, efficiency, and profitability of various marketing channels (e.g., Google Ads, Meta Ads, Blog, Email). By analyzing raw marketing spend and revenue data, this project extracts critical multi-touch attribution insights and calculates foundational growth metrics like CPA (Cost Per Acquisition) and ROAS (Return on Ad Spend) to help businesses optimize their ad budgets.
